+Feature: Tide prediction edge cases
+
+  @captain
+  Scenario: Invalid date string input produces no result
+    Given the tide table for Fundy Cove
+    When I ask for the next high tide after "not-a-date"
+    Then the prediction fails with a TypeError
+
+  @captain
+  Scenario: Empty tides array produces no result
+    Given an empty tide table
+    When I ask for the next high tide after "2026-07-12T05:00:00Z"
+    Then the prediction fails with "no upcoming high tide in data"
+
+  @captain
+  Scenario: Low-tide entries do not satisfy high-tide query
+    Given the tide table for Fundy Cove
+    When I ask for the next high tide after "2026-07-12T10:30:00Z"
+    Then the predicted high tide is at "2026-07-12T16:45:00Z" with height 4.5
